---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-slate-200 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 text-sm text-slate-500">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
          <span class="inline-flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500 to-brand-700 text-white text-xs">AI</span>
          AI 工具集
        </div>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">发现与分享好用的 AI 工具，提供实用在线小工具。每日更新。</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">导航</div>
        <ul class="space-y-1">
          <li><a href={`${base}`} class="hover:text-brand-600">首页</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${base}ai-tools`} class="hover:text-brand-600">AI 工具榜单</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${base}tools`} class="hover:text-brand-600">在线工具</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${base}about`} class="hover:text-brand-600">关于</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">声明</div>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">本站工具列表中部分链接为合作推广链接，通过这些链接购买可能获得佣金。工具信息仅供参考。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 pt-4 border-t border-slate-200 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-2">
      <span>© {year} AI 工具集. 保留所有权利.</span>
      <span class="text-xs">由 WorkBuddy 自动维护</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
